cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL. 

The paper is about scene labeling, which is a computer vision task, so cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely category. The paper proposes a new type of recurrent neural network (RNN) for this task, so cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are also likely categories. The paper also introduces an attention model, which is a popular technique in natural language processing (NLP), so cs.CL (Computation and Language) is a possible category. Finally, the paper uses convolutional neural networks (CNNs), which are a common tool in deep learning, so cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is another possible category.
